<div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center">
  <div class="bg-[url('pattern.svg')] absolute -z-50 opacity-5 top-0 blur-sm w-full h-screen"></div>
  <div class="w-full h-28 blur-md opacity-50 absolute top-0 -z-40 bg-white rounded-b-md"></div>
  <div class="flex items-center flex-col space-y-6 mt-24">
    <h1 class="flex text-5xl font-bold text-purple-700">
      Bem vindo ao Finance
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 w-2/6 text-center">Seja para gerenciar despesas, acompanhar ganhos ou simplesmente ter um controle financeiro mais sólido, é a solução ideal para suas necessidades financeiras. A aplicação oferece uma maneira simples e eficaz de registrar e visualizar suas finanças mensais</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 flex space-x-4">
    <%= link_to "Começar", "/receipt", class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 bg-purple-600 text-gray-50 hover:bg-purple-600/90 px-4 py-2", role: "button" %>
    <% if !session[:current_user_id].present? %>
      <%= link_to "Registrar-se", "/user/new", class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 border border-purple-300 bg-white text-purple-600 hover:border-purple-600/90 px-4 py-2", role: "button" %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
